      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧桂英、萧恩上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "江边俱是打鱼家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "树直哪怕日影斜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "青山绿水难描画"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青山绿水难描画"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "父女打鱼在河下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "家贫哪怕人笑咱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可怜我年迈苍苍气力不佳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "桂英儿掌舟舵父把网撒"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹年迈，这河下生意不作也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本当不作河下生意，怎奈你我父女拿什么度日呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要啼哭，将船栓在柳荫之下为父要凉爽凉爽啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，二位贤弟慢走，愚兄不远送了！这才是我的好朋友！哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹上船来吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，爹爹，此二位叔叔他是甚等样人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，儿问的是他？儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忆昔当年擒方腊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倪荣、李俊二豪侠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "弟兄们双双走天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "蟒袍玉带不愿挂"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蟒袍玉带不愿挂"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "昔日有个俞伯牙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "千里迢迢访豪家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "知心人儿说的是知心话"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "猛抬头见红日坠落西斜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "知心人儿说的是知心话"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，儿啊，你看天色不早，你我父女回去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，待我收拾收拾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父女打鱼在江下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家贫哪怕人笑咱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看看不觉红日落，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一轮明月照芦花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧恩、萧桂英同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
