    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "大教师",
        "家丁",
        "萧恩",
        "萧桂英"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧恩上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "昨夜晚吃酒醉和衣而卧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将身儿来至在草堂打坐，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧桂英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "遭不幸我的母早年亡故，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹请来用茶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为父不叫你渔家打扮，怎么还是这样的渔家的打扮呐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，爹爹，女儿生在渔家，长在渔船。不叫女儿渔家打扮，是要怎样的打扮呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯。不听教训就是不孝哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，爹爹，不必生气，女儿改过就是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这便才是啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大教师、家丁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别走啦！到了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就这儿？我去瞧瞧去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么没在家呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "关着门呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诶，关着门是在家呢！锁着门才没在家呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这叫去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫门我们不会，瞧您的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这也得瞧我的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使点劲呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使劲不让他听见了吗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为的是要他听见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，为的是叫他听见？等我脱了衣裳啊。瞅见没有？这叫门得有个架势，这叫"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧桂英下。萧恩开门，推大教师倒地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，这是谁泼的水啊？滑了我一个跟头啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦！萧恩出来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "萧恩出来啦？我瞧瞧去哦！哟呵，糟老头子！咱们跟他横着点！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你是哪里来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们是丁府上来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是丁府上的教师爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，这老头子会两下子啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们给请安来啦！问好来啦！催讨渔税银子地来啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来为此。你来看，这几日天旱水浅，鱼不上网。改日有了银钱，送上府去，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么着？你说什么这两天天旱水浅，鱼不上网。改日有了银钱，给我们爷们儿"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旁人来啦，倒还罢了，今日教师爷你来了么？哈哈哈！越发的无有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "照我看呐，要钱没有。你认识这个不认识？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝廷王法，要它何用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么朝廷王法，这是你姥姥怕你活的不长远，给你打的百家锁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放屁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，没打着，锁上，拉着就走啊！萧恩呐！要钱没有，教师爷我要锁你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？尔要讲锁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要讲锁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！你就与我锁锁锁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大教师以锁链套萧恩，反被萧恩兜回套住脖子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦！锁他拉着走。怎么锁我也拉着走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拉错了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又拉错啦！来，拿着，用不着这个！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "话倒是两句好话，可惜你二大爷无有工夫啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二大爷啦啊？跟你要钱，你是没有，让你跟我们走，你又不走。教师爷带的人"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？尔要讲打么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要讲打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！老汉幼年之间，听见“打架”二字，好象似小孩子盼新年穿新鞋的一般。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这呀撇鞋，你说什么你幼年间听说打架如同那小孩子穿新鞋过新年的一般？教"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比作何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好比那耗子舔猫的鼻梁骨——我要作死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？听你之言，敢莫是当真讲打？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然讲打？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然讲打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娃娃！待老汉将衣帽丢在家中，打个样儿与你们见识见识！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言气得我七孔冒火！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言气得你七孔冒火！今儿教师爷我打你个八处生烟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只气得年迈人咬碎牙窝。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧恩打家丁。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在江湖叫萧恩不才是我！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么的？在江湖叫萧恩不才是你？教师爷我也有个名有个姓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔叫什么东西？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人嘛！怎么东西！我叫“左铜锤”！哎呀，锤上喽！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "大战场小战场见过许多。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧恩打家丁。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说什么？你好比出山虎独自一个？教师爷我好比那打猎的，单打你这个出山"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尔好比看家犬一群一窝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！怎么揪我的耳朵呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你本是奴下奴敢来欺我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "别打啦！人家骂啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "家丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骂你一人儿奴下奴！没有我们四个人儿什么事情！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的，你们四个人倒摘得挺干净呐。我问问他去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就便是三狗头，你二大爷何惧呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人头怎么改了狗头啦？你那儿有功夫吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这里来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！你站稳了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大教师撞三羊头。萧恩领起，打家丁下，截住大教师，大教师欲跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！起来！起来！起来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得，您让我过去得了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！闻听教师爷武艺高强！老汉今日倒要领教领教啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领教什么呀？我是这马勺苍蝇混饭吃！你让我过去得啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "总要领教！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "总要领教？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我练两手你瞧瞧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你且练来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你瞧这个！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挑水的扁担。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "您再瞧这个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "砸煤的锤子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "越发的不好！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领教什么呀？我是这马勺苍蝇混饭吃！你让我过去得啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！慢来！打尔三拳头，放尔过去呃！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三拳头？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我连三指头也经不住啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "总要打的！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "总要打？你别忙，等我运运气！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这作什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我这儿搂把呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "招打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！慢着，你把这孤丁去了，改押躺怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧桂英上，打大教师。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大教师",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的！你们俩打一个呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大教师下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，爹爹！看孩儿打得可好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打得好！打出祸来了！快取为父衣帽过来。去到丁府，抢他个原告儿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依女儿之见，不去的好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快取来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好看守门户，为父去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧恩下，萧桂英下。）"
        }
      ],
