    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "萧恩",
        "萧桂英"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧桂英上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的父强上告输赢未准，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧恩上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恼恨那吕子秋为官不正，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忽听门外有人声，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹为何这等模样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀儿呀！为父上得堂去，那贼一言不问，将为父重责，喂呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼子呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "骂一声贼子真可恨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，爹爹你、你、你受了屈了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这还不叫做受屈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎样才算受屈呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那贼言道：叫为父连夜过江，与他赔罪。那时才叫做受屈呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹你还是去也不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！为父恨不得飞过江，我就杀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噤声！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀尔的满门。方消为父心头之恨呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹呀！他家势力浩大，你、你、你还是忍耐了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你小孩子家，晓得什么？快取为父衣帽戒刀过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹，依女儿看来，还是不去的好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用你管，快快取来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好好看守门户，为父去也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹请转！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女儿跟随爹爹前去如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女流之辈，不去也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爹爹杀人，孩儿站在一旁，与爹爹助助胆量，也是好的呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既要前去，带好儿自己的戒刀，随为父的走啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。啊！爹爹请转！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这门还未曾关呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这门么？关也罢，不关也罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "里面还有许多动用家具呢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门都不关，要家具何用？不明白的冤家呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不必啼哭，儿呀，庆顶珠可在身旁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在身旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此甚好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（萧恩、萧桂英同上船。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想这夜晚之间，比不得白昼，儿要掌稳了舵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恼恨那吕子秋行事可恶，"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的儿因何故撒了蓬索？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，爹爹，此番过江，杀人是真的还是假的啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自然是真的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女儿心中害怕，我、我不去了啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！不叫儿前来，儿偏偏要来，船行半江之中，也罢！待为父将你送回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧桂英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女儿舍不得爹爹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
